original_title: 世間知らず女子大生ナンパ 可愛いくてチヤホヤされている甘ちゃん女子を大人のルールに引きずり込め!!
overview: We spotlighted a female college student who is looking for a job during the employment ice age! They are relaxed and of the Internet generation. Too sweet to go out into society! Therefore, we pretended to support the job-hunting college students who picked them up, and taught them the harsh reality of adult society! ! Picking Up Naive Female College Students, Drag The Cute And Cheerful Sweet Girls To The Rules Of Adults! ! Cast: 5 ignorant female college students looking for a job during the employment ice age Yui Hatano, Mayu Kurume
title: Pick Up Naive College Student. Involve Pretty and Spoiled Girls in Adult Rule!!
